{"tid":921103,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"訓左冇睇, 波叔個仔代理個咩鳩T Plus 收到10 張票未","createTime":"2018-11-29T10:02:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-29T10:02:32.000Z","uid":59746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"1aa365c08392bfbe60e1ee5e750784b9074104ef","tid":921103,"uid":59746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T10:02:32.000Z","msg":"「龍床盤」菁雋截至下午4時暫收不足10票<br />\n<br />\n內房佳源國際牽頭持有的「龍床盤」屯門菁雋，以高價出擊，開放式定價呎價22,214元貴絕新界西北。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static01.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2215000/2219466/TP_02_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2215000%2F2219466%2FTP_02_1024.jpg&h=d17083b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n截至下午4時，現場售樓處冷清，市場消息指暫收票不足10票，據悉只有3客入票，以首批73伙，距離足額亦有一段距離。<br />\n<br />\n菁雋首張價單涉73伙，戶型由開放式至2房，實用面積131至416平方呎，定價285萬至928.8萬元，呎價13,452至22,327元，價單市值約3.2億元，惟項目中最細的128平方呎單位則未有推出。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ps.hket.com/article/2219466/%E3%80%8C%E9%BE%8D%E5%BA%8A%E7%9B%A4%E3%80%8D%E8%8F%81%E9%9B%8B%E6%88%AA%E8%87%B3%E4%B8%8B%E5%8D%884%E6%99%82%E6%9A%AB%E6%94%B6%E4%B8%8D%E8%B6%B310%E7%A5%A8?mtc=90025\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fps.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2219466%2F%25E3%2580%258C%25E9%25BE%258D%25E5%25BA%258A%25E7%259B%25A4%25E3%2580%258D%25E8%258F%2581%25E9%259B%258B%25E6%2588%25AA%25E8%2587%25B3%25E4%25B8%258B%25E5%258D%25884%25E6%2599%2582%25E6%259A%25AB%25E6%2594%25B6%25E4%25B8%258D%25E8%25B6%25B310%25E7%25A5%25A8%3Fmtc%3D90025&d=JMapTl%2F%2BfFbrePG30TsOpTCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=823762aa\" target=\"_blank\">https://ps.hket.com/article/2219466/%E3%80%8C%E9%BE%8D%E5%BA%8A%E7%9B%A4%E3%80%8D%E8%8F%81%E9%9B%8B%E6%88%AA%E8%87%B3%E4%B8%8B%E5%8D%884%E6%99%82%E6%9A%AB%E6%94%B6%E4%B8%8D%E8%B6%B310%E7%A5%A8?mtc=90025</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">絕對有資格問鼎本世紀最柒新盤</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}